      <item>
        <title>Typography</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;We have two core fonts: &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Realtime Text&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Proxima Nova&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Realtime Text is used for titles and elements (such as buttons), whereas Proxima Nova is used for paragraph text.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Title classes use the Greek alphabet as a naming convention. This allows the styled heading to be seperated from the semantic tag.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example, an H1 and an H6 with a &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;title--gamma&lt;/code&gt; class, will both visually look the same.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;pattern&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h1 class=&quot;title--alpha pattern-item&quot;&gt;Page title (28px)&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;h2 class=&quot;title--beta pattern-item&quot;&gt;Section title - (24px)&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;h3 class=&quot;title--gamma pattern-item&quot;&gt;Section sub-title - (22px)&lt;/h3&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;h4 class=&quot;title--delta pattern-item&quot;&gt;Paragraph title - (18px)&lt;/h4&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;h5 class=&quot;title--epsilon pattern-item&quot;&gt;Paragraph sub-title - (16px)&lt;/h5&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;h6 class=&quot;title--zeta pattern-item&quot;&gt;Paragraph heading - (12px)&lt;/h6&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;h1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;title--alpha&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;H1 - Page title&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/h1&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;h2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;title--beta&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;H2 - Section title&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;h3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;title--delta&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;H3 - Section sub-title&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/h3&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;h4&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;title--gamma&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;H4 - Paragraph title&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/h4&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;h5&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;title--epsilon&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;H5 - Paragraph sub-title&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/h5&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;h6&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;title--zeta&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;H6 - Paragraph heading&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/h6&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;utility-classes&quot;&gt;Utility Classes&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;These classes provide a quick way to change text color and alignment.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;pattern&quot;&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-primary&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the primary color&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-developer&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the developer color&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-beta&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the beta color&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-snow&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the neutral snow color&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-smoke&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the neutral smoke color&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-silver&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the neutral silver color&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-slate&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the neutral slate color&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-black&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the neutral black color&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-danger&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the ui danger color&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-warning&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the ui warning color&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;u-color-success&quot;&gt;I will always be colored with the ui success color&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-primary&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the primary color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-developer&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the developer color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-beta&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the beta color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-snow&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the neutral snow color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-smoke&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the neutral smoke color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-silver&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the neutral silver color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-slate&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the neutral slate color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-black&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the neutral black color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-danger&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the ui danger color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-warning&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the ui warning color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-color-success&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will always be colored with the ui success color&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;pattern u-text-align-center&quot;&gt;
  &lt;span&gt;I will be aligned centrally on desktop and tablet, and left aligned on mobile&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-text-align-center&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will be aligned centrally on desktop and tablet, and left aligned on mobile&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;pattern u-text-align-right&quot;&gt;
  &lt;span&gt;I will be aligned to the right&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;u-text-align-right&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;I will be aligned to the right&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
